      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·小雅·谷風之什·005.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">北山.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>陟彼北山，言采其杞。偕偕士子，朝夕從事。王事靡盬，憂我父母。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>I ascend that northern hill,
And gather the medlars.
An officer, strong and vigorous,
Morning and evening I am engaged in service.
The king's business is not to be slackly performed;
And my parents are left in sorrow.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__xiaoya-gufeng-005__002__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sheking-1871-ocr">
      <prop type="x-work-id">shijing</prop>
