      <prop type="x-alignment-granularity">stanza</prop>
      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">0.99</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·小雅·谷風之什·005.2</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">北山.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>溥天之下，莫非王土。率土之濱，莫非王臣。大夫不均，我從事獨賢。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Under the wide heaven,
All is the king's land.
Within the sea-boundaries of the land,
All are the king's servants.
His great officers are unfair, --
Making me serve thus as if I alone were worthy.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__xiaoya-gufeng-005__003__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sheking-1871-ocr">
      <prop type="x-work-id">shijing</prop>
