      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·小雅·谷風之什·005.6</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">北山.6</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>或湛樂飲酒，或慘慘畏咎；或出入風議，或靡事不為。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Some indulge long in pleasure and drinking,
And some are miserable, in apprehension of blame;
Some, at home and abroad, pass critical remarks,
And some have everything to do.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
